{"title":"Smith Relaunches Ultralite Sunglasses to Celebrate 60 Years in Style!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/smith-relaunches-ultralite-sunglasses-to-celebrate-60-years-in-style/","date":1738357846000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-101-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"SMITH - Ultralight with helmet\" /></p>\n<p>Smith has been around for 60 years now, and to celebrate, they’re relaunching a style from the past. That would be 1987 to be exact, when the Ultralite sunglasses were the freshest shades on the scene. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many of those style points from the 80’s are coming back around, so what better time for Smith to dig into the archive and refresh a classic. The retro ski goggle-inspired oversized shades have a classic cylindrical shield lens with a slight wraparound curve and ventilation holes to keep things chill. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"2304\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-1536x2304.webp\" alt=\"SMITH - Ultralight on male model\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-1536x2304.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-200x300.webp 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-80x120.webp 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-768x1152.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-1024x1536.webp 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-1365x2048.webp 1365w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith-UltraLight-AndyHardy-27-scaled.webp 1707w\" /></a></figure>\n<figcaption>(Photos/Andy Hardy/Smith)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>KEY FEATURES</p>\n\n\n\n<p>• ChromaPop<img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2122.png\" alt=\"™\" /> lenses enhance contrast and natural color to make the details pop • Evolve<img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2122.png\" alt=\"™\" /> bio-based frame material is lightweight and durable<br />• Goggle-inspired strap compatible temple tips<br />• Archive Collection fleece pouch</p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Medium to large fit, XL coverage<br />• 6-base cylindrical shield lens curvature<br />• AutoLock hinges hold frames open for easy one-hand on and off<br />• Adjustable Megol nose pads provide non-slip grip so glasses stay put</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Tortoise_CHROMAPOP-GRAY-GREEN_3Q.png\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Tortoise_CHROMAPOP-GRAY-GREEN_3Q-1536x1536.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Tortoise_CHROMAPOP-GRAY-GREEN_3Q-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Tortoise_CHROMAPOP-GRAY-GREEN_3Q-297x297.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Tortoise_CHROMAPOP-GRAY-GREEN_3Q-120x120.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Tortoise_CHROMAPOP-GRAY-GREEN_3Q-768x768.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Tortoise_CHROMAPOP-GRAY-GREEN_3Q.png 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Malachite_CHROMAPOP-LOW-LIGHT-COPPER_3Q.png\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Smith_Ultralite_Matte_Malachite_CHROMAPOP-LOW-LIGHT-COPPER_3Q-1536x1536.png\" alt=\"SMITH - Ultralight malachite\" srcset=\"h